Txt_Registration_UI_Warrior_Info.Text: Wielders of weighty weapons; warriors use their strength and stamina to deal out damage and defend their allies.

Txt_Registration_UI_Mage_Info.Text: Master spell casters; mages harness their wealth of magical knowledge to take care of foes foolish enough to stand in their way.

Txt_Registration_UI_Priest_Info.Text: The best backup any adventurer could ask for; priests can cast healing spells and also wield weapons.

Txt_Registration_UI_MartialArtist_Info.Text: Masters of hand-to-hand combat; martial artists are amazingly agile and can land critical hits for fun.

Txt_Registration_UI_Merchant_Info.Text: Experts in commerce; merchants make themselves useful by gathering gold coins and appraising items.

Txt_Registration_UI_Gadabout_Info.Text: The life of the party; gadabouts can cause all sorts of things to happen with their wild high jinks.

Txt_Registration_UI_Sage_Info.Text: Beings who have more or less nothing left to learn; sages can use both mage- and priest-specific spells.

Txt_Registration_UI_Thief_Info.Text: Sneaky so-and-sos; thieves are excellent at avoiding enemies in dungeons and sniffing out treasure.

Txt_Registration_UI_MonsterTamer_Info.Text: Oddballs who steal most of their moves from their monster mates, combining them to create an inimitable fighting style.

Txt_Registration_UI_HairSelect_Guide.Text: Choose the colour of their hair.

Txt_Registration_Message_Start.Text: *: Welcome to Premiere Adventurer Listing Services! With PALS, you're sure to build a winning team!

Txt_Registration_Message_First.Text:
*: We're here to help you get the hottest adventuring talent out there off the dole and onto your roster!<KEY_WAIT>
*: Just tell us what you're looking for, and we'll deliver a qualified professional direct to the Party Planning counter!

Txt_Registration_Message_Top.Text: *: So, are you looking to bolster your roster with some fresh blood today?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_NameSelect.Text: *: And what kind of person are you looking for, exactly? Why don't you give me a name, and we'll take it from there?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_JobSelect.Text: *: Alright. Now tell me what kind of vocation you'd like them to have.<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_StyleSelect.Text: *: Could you tell me a bit more about them?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_LooksSelect.Text: *: And what do they look like?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_HairColorSelect.Text: *: Alright. What colour is their hair?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_Confirm_01.Text: *: Ah-ha! I think I have just what you're looking for. Does this candidate seem like a good fit for your team?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_UseSeedFirst.Text:
*: It's your lucky day, {LEADER}!<KEY_WAIT>
*: As part of His Majesty's Special Adventurer Programme, you've qualified for a Supplementary Educational Enhancement Dispensation!<KEY_WAIT>
*: It takes the form of five attribute-enhancing SEEDs<--->or <6>seeds<9><--->which will give your team members a much-needed boost!<KEY_WAIT>
*: You can choose the seeds yourself, or allow me to use my career guidance skills to pick for you.<KEY_WAIT>
*: If you pick for yourself, you can select up to five seeds of your choice for your new-found friend. But if you let me pick, I'll be providing a comprehensive service, and applying the seeds as I see fit.

Txt_Registration_Message_UseSeedSelect.Text: *: So, how will you be distributing {WORD}'s seed allowance?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_UseSeedStart.Text:
*: You have {VALUE} left to use.
Think smart, now!

Txt_Registration_Message_UseSeedAuto.Text:
*: Excellent.
Just leave it to me!

Txt_Registration_Message_Confirm_02.Text: *: So you're after someone like {WORD}, then?

Txt_Registration_Message_VoiceSelect.Text: *: Last but not least, can you give me an idea of what they sound like?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_FinishConfirm.Text: *: If you back out now, they won't actually join your party. Are you sure you want to stop here?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_Confirm_03.Text:
*: So, you'll be recruiting {WORD}.
Is that alright with you?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_AddBarMember.Text: *: Lovely. {WORD} ought to be waiting for you downstairs.

Txt_Registration_Message_AddRegistration.Text: *: Will you be looking to recruit anybody else today?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_BarMemberMax.Text: *: I'm afraid you'll need to let somebody go if you want to recruit anyone else. Is that alright with you?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_DeleteBarMember.Text: *: So, which member of your team do you think would...ahem...benefit from a new challenge?<NO_INPUT>
*: So you'll be saying goodbye to {WORD}, will you? Are you sure? There's no unfiring someone...<NO_INPUT>

*: Well, it's sad to let anyone go, but I'm confident this will be good for {WORD}'s personal development.<KEY_WAIT>
*: And don't worry<--->we took care to reclaim all relevant assets before escorting your former employee from the premises. Everything should now be safely in your bag.<KEY_WAIT>
*: And with {WORD}'s departure, that's a space on your roster freed up<--->meaning you can recruit some exciting new talent!

*: Changed your mind, have you?
Well, you never know<--->it might be for the best.

Txt_Registration_Message_NameError_Dupli.Text: *: Oh, that's strange... I think this person's already on your team. Shall we look for another candidate for you instead?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_NameError_Ban.Text:
*: I'm sorry, but we donâ€™t have anyone by that name on our books.<KEY_WAIT>
*: Shall we look for another candidate for you instead?<NO_INPUT>

Txt_Registration_Message_NameError_Roto.Text:
*: E-Erdrick!? You did say Erdrick, didn't you? I'm terribly sorry... But <6>Erdrick,<9> isn't just a name, you know<--->it's a title.<KEY_WAIT>
*: It actually means <6>dwelling-land<9> in the language of the ancients.<KEY_WAIT>
*: So when you call someone Erdrick, you're literally acknowledging them as the land's anointed representative<--->its champion.<KEY_WAIT>
*: Needless to say, only the greatest of heroes are permitted to bear the moniker. And I'm forbidden to seek out such anointed souls. It's more than my job's worth!

Txt_Registration_Message_RegistrationFin.Text: *: Just come and see me again whenever you're in the market for some top-flight adventuring talent. Bye now!
